         "text" : {
            "headline" : "Comment added by Paul Trost",
            "text" : "I spoke to Stacy about this, and given that EA4 is having so many issues right now, we want to use EA3 currently. You can add LDAP support to EA3 pretty easily. This URL describes it:<br>http://www.watters.ws/mediawiki/index.php/PHP_LDAP_module_for_cPanel_servers<br><br>We should keep a Makefile for EA4 as well that has the commands to install the allphp profile (not the RPM install line), so we know what to run in the future when EA4 is stable."
         },
